data.description: If you are looking for a brick ranch, located on 3.56 ACRES, in an established rural neighborhood, that has easy access to Pageland area amenities, this one may be for you!  It features a spacious living room leading to the front covered porch, kitchen/dining room, that leads to the enclosed rear porch, laundry/mud room with direct access to the side load two car garage/storage, primary bedroom/bathroom, and two other bedrooms with easy access to the full hall bathroom. There is a rear fenced yard area, detached storage, along with lots of room to roam on this acreage!
